f%a9%e7%b0%a1%2c1147%2c20220630%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,審簡,1147,20220630,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"審簡","JNO":"1147","JDATE":"20220630","JTITLE":"家庭暴力罪之傷害"}